<topic id='attribute_accommodation_status_code.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Attribute: ACCOMMODATION STATUS CODE - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
An indication of the type of accommodation that a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 currently has. This should be based on the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>'s main or permanent residence.        </p>
      <p>Notes:</p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATIONS</xref>
               <p>
 may choose to collect the 
                                <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_accommodation_status_code">ACCOMMODATION STATUS CODE</xref>
 codes at the high level (National Codes ending in "0") or at the more detailed level below each high-level code.                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
The following National Codes have been introduced to add further granularity to National Code CJ03 
                                <i>'<xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                           keyref="business_definition_young_offender_institution">Young Offender Institution</xref>'</i>. However, National Code CJ03 is still valid where extra detail cannot be collected:                    </p>
            </div>
            <ul>
               <li>
                  <div>
                     <p>
CJ05 
                                            <i>'<xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                                 keyref="business_definition_young_offender_institution__15-17_">Young Offender Institution (15-17)</xref>'</i>
                     </p>
                  </div>
               </li>
               <li>
                  <div>
                     <p>
CJ06 
                                            <i>'<xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                                 keyref="business_definition_young_offender_institution__18-21_">Young Offender Institution (18-21)</xref>'.                                </i>
                     </p>
                  </div>
               </li>
            </ul>
         </li>
      </ul>
  </div>
</body>
